'''殺傷鏈'''在軍事上指的是一種攻击過程，具體是指识别所要打擊的目标、向目标派遣兵力、决定并下令攻击目标、最后摧毁目标等一系列攻擊過程<ref>{{Cite web|title=Kill Chain Approach|url=http://cno.navylive.dodlive.mil/2013/04/23/kill-chain-approach-4/|date=April 23, 2013|work=Chief of Naval Operations|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130613233413/http://cno.navylive.dodlive.mil/2013/04/23/kill-chain-approach-4/|archivedate=June 13, 2013}}</ref>。而[[洛克希德·马丁|洛克希德·马丁公司]]将这一攻擊過程引入[[信息安全|信息安全]]領域，假想實施计算机网络入侵的[[黑客|黑客]]也會採取這種攻擊過程，並將其稱之為网络杀伤链模型<ref>{{Cite web|title=How Lockheed Martin's 'Kill Chain' Stopped SecurID Attack|url=http://www.darkreading.com/attacks-breaches/how-lockheed-martins-kill-chain-stopped-securid-attack/d/d-id/1139125|accessdate=June 30, 2016|author=Higgins, Kelly Jackson|date=January 12, 2013|work=DARKReading|archive-date=2021-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129015517/https://www.darkreading.com/attacks-breaches/how-lockheed-martins-kill-chain-stopped-securid-attack/d/d-id/1139125|dead-url=no}}</ref>。网络杀伤链模型在信息安全界得到了一定的采用<ref>{{cite web|title=Leveraging The Kill Chain For Awesome|url=http://www.darkreading.com/attacks-breaches/leveraging-the-kill-chain-for-awesome/a/d-id/1317810|accessdate=June 30, 2016|author=Mason, Sean|date=December 2, 2014|work=DARKReading|archive-date=2020-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202225725/https://www.darkreading.com/attacks-breaches/leveraging-the-kill-chain-for-awesome/a/d-id/1317810|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，这一模型并没有得到普遍接受，批评者认为这一模型存在根本性的缺陷<ref>{{Cite web|title=The practicality of the Cyber Kill Chain approach to security|url=http://www.csoonline.com/article/2134037/strategic-planning-erm/the-practicality-of-the-cyber-kill-chain-approach-to-security.html|accessdate=June 30, 2016|author=Myers, Lysa|date=October 4, 2013|work=CSO Online|archive-date=2017-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170828050249/http://www.csoonline.com/article/2134037/strategic-planning-erm/the-practicality-of-the-cyber-kill-chain-approach-to-security.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 

